videos.headline: Smith puts Minnesota on the board with short TD
videos.description: Rodney Smith finds an opening and runs three yards for a Minnesota touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith puts Minnesota on the board with short TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Langan picked off for 2nd time
videos.description: Johnny Langan tries to find a receiver, but Phillip Howard hauls it in for the Minnesota interception.

videos.headline: Morgan, Bateman connect to pad Minnesota's lead
videos.description: Tanner Morgan throws to Rashod Bateman in the end zone for a 13-yard touchdown, giving Minnesota a 14-0 lead over Rutgers.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Morgan, Bateman connect to pad Minnesota’s lead) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Smith scampers 16 yards for his second TD
videos.description: On Minnesota's opening drive of the second half, Rodney Smith navigates through the Rutgers defense for a 16-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith scampers 16 yards for his second TD) 2019/10/19

videos.headline: Winfield returns pick-six for Minnesota
videos.description: Antoine Winfield Jr. picks off Johnny Langan for the second time and goes 33 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Cancer survivor O'Brien gets into first Minnesota game
videos.description: Four-time cancer survivor Casey O'Brien gets into his first Minnesota game as a holder and has an emotional embrace with PJ Fleck after.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cancer survivor O'Brien gets into first Minnesota game) 2019/10/19
